SafeCast.metadata: {"compiler":{"version":"0.8.17+commit.8df45f5f"},"language":"Solidity","output":{"abi":[],"devdoc":{"details":"Wrappers over Solidity's uintXX/intXX casting operators with added overflow checks. Downcasting from uint256/int256 in Solidity does not revert on overflow.
